The paper deals with content-based image retrieval, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed algorithm involves combining the Pareto front method with efficient manifold ranking, which suggests a potential connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM).
